                            <comment id="13423919" author="cmenzel" created="Fri, 27 Jul 2012 15:16:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;With &amp;lt;wicket:link&amp;gt; it works, since that introduces a container component.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13423952" author="cmenzel" created="Fri, 27 Jul 2012 16:20:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;6.x is not affected.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I fixed it in 1.5.x by having AutoLinkResolver trying getAssociatedMarkup first before using getMarkup. That way it uses the correct scope to resolve package resources.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
